 -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

Description
-=-=-=-=-=-=

The latest version of the Number 1 puzzle craze!
The rules are simple- each numer from 1 to 9 should be used only once in each row, column and 3 by 3 square. The puzzle is 

completed when there are no more unknown squares. But don't worry you don't need to be a mathematical genius to play, each 

of the puzzles is solved using pure logic. Sudoku Classic 2 has three difficulty levels- Beginner, Intermediate and 

Advanced, providing hours of challenging fun for all ages & ability levels!

Additional Details
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

Features:

* 3 difficulty levels- Beginner, Intermediate and Advanced
* Simple 'drag and drop' play
* Save and restart at any stage
* Undo to last incorrect move or go back to beginning
* Hints and tips (and cheat when you get stuck)
* Timer- try and beat your best time!
* Print & Go facility for bus, plane or train
* These genuine hand crafted games play better than computer generated ones- and no guessing!
* Over 400,000 copies of version 1 sold!
* Multilingual interfaces; English, French, German, Spanish, Italian, Dutch, Portuguese and Swedish
